ing that is now _actually_ accurate and is pruned once-per-week. So now your "Followers" count, even across pods **will** be accurate and up-to-date ğŸ¥³â€¨- **FIXED** Finally squished that annoying bug ğŸ causing profile data to flip-flopâ€¨- **FIXED** The `LookupHandler()` was fixed to support auto/tab-completion for external feeds! ğŸ¥³â€¨- **UPDATE** Update Chinese and Taiwanese translations! ğŸ‡¨ğŸ‡³ ğŸ‡¹ğŸ‡¼â€¨â€¨Big thanks to @gbmor for driving the need for some much needed network optimizations!â€¨Thanks again to @ullarah for the many UI/UX updates and improvements! ğŸ™‡â€â™‚ï¸â€¨And thank you again to @venjiang for updating the CN and TW translations! ğŸ‘Œâ€¨â€¨As per usual, please provide feedback to @<prologic https://twtxt.net/user/prologic/twtxt.txt> or reply to this Yarn ğŸ¤—
